item.title: Getting Started
item.description: For information on how to install SiriDB, please visit the SiriDB Server github page. For information on how to create a new database or expand an existing database, please visit the SiriDB Admin github page. Other SiriDB projects: SiriDB Prompt is a terminal based SiriDB client with auto-completion support. SiriDB HTTP provides an optional web interface and HTTP API for SiriDB. SiriDB Connector C (libsiridb) is a native SiriDB connector for the C language.
